![Episode59.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578251534897-HV8J2OSQ7NPOCP8JYZSS/Episode59.jpg)

With 2018 firmly in our rear-view, we are honored to bring you the Best of 2018 CBC Awards! It's definitely been a hell of a year when it comes to comic book media and this episode highlights the best and brightest things to come last year. Not only do we get to talk about each deserving nominee, but the winners were chosen by the members of the CLIQUE and all winners will be the result of popular vote. See who's left holding the golden trophies when the dust settles in this fancy-smancy episode of the Major Issues Podcast!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

